# Sheets â€“ Electronic Systems (Part II: Oscillators & Regulators)

This folder contains problem sheets and detailed solutions for **Part II** of the *Electronic Systems* course, covering waveform generation and voltage regulation circuits.

## Topics Covered

- RC and LC Oscillator design  
- Wien Bridge and Crystal Oscillators  
- Monostable, Bistable, and Astable Multivibrators  
- Frequency and timing control in multivibrators  
- Zener-based and IC voltage regulators  
- Load and line regulation calculations
